		<p class="copy3"><span class="copy3bold">The AT&amp;T Statistical Dialog Toolkit V1.0</span><br />
	
	
			<a href="/people/Williams_Jason_D/index.html " class="">Jason Williams</a><br />
	
	
	
	

	
		IEEE Speech and Language Processing Technical Committee Newsletter,&nbsp;
		

	

	

	<!--  -->
	<!--  -->
	<!--  -->
	<!--  -->

	
	

	
		IEEE Speech and Language Processing Technical Committee Newsletter,&nbsp;
		

	

	

	

	

	
		
	

	
			2010.&nbsp;
		


	
	
	
	<a href="/techdocs/TD_100016.html?section=pub" target="_new">[BIB]</a>
	
	
	
	
	<div id="abstract_1" style="display: none" class="copy3">The AT&T Statistical Dialog Toolkit V1.0 is now available to the research community.  This toolkit simplifies building statistical dialog systems, which maintain a distribution over multiple dialog states.</div>
	







 
